      "name": "Mesh convergence and discretisation error study (2023)",
      "description": "Richardson extrapolation applied across three mesh densities (4.2 M, 9.8 M, 21.5 M cells). Grid convergence index below 2.1% for all wall-shear-stress quantities of interest at adult operating conditions. Study conducted in 2023; mesh parameters unchanged for subsequent production runs including any paediatric-range simulations.",
      "generatedAtTime": "2023-07-22T00:00:00Z"
