      "acceptanceCriteria": "Version-controlled solver with documented release notes and regression test suite sufficient for MRL 2.",
      "rationale": "ANSYS Fluent 2023R1 used under an FDA-recognised software quality management plan. Version control and regression testing records reviewed and found compliant with MRL 2 requirements."
    },
    {
      "factorStandard": "ASME-VV40-2018",
      "factorType": "Numerical code verification",
      "type": "CredibilityFactor",
      "requiredLevel": 1,
