    "type": "DecisionRecord",
    "actor": "https://uofa.net/synth/actor/morrison-credibility-team",
    "role": "Credibility assessment team",
    "outcome": "Accepted",
    "rationale": "All seven assessed credibility factors meet or exceed required levels for MRL 2. The six non-assessed factors are appropriately scoped out at MRL 2 per ASME V&V 40 Table 4. The 2023 adult validation campaign demonstrates CFD hemolysis predictions within ±12% of experimental measurements across the original operating envelope. The team accepted the argument that non-dimensional shear-stress similarity between the adult lower boundary (2.0 L/min) and the paediatric upper boundary (1.2 L/min) provides adequate coverage of the expanded envelope introduced by the Q3 2025 label update, without requiring new experimental validation runs. The overall credibility is assessed as sufficient to support the Accepted decision at Medium assurance level.",
